00:24:13,560 --> 00:24:15,520
I'm so weak, in fact,
我實在很軟弱

331
00:24:15,600 --> 00:24:20,360
that I'm scared of opening those boxes and running into the old Nevra in them.
我不敢打開那些盒子，然後又變成以前的內芙拉

